        "heading_beBkyN": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "From Seed to Sanctuary",
            "heading_size": "hd3",
            "heading_highlight_style": "none"
          }
        },
        "text_FqxBbK": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>In a world of constant motion, MIORA carves out spaces for stillness and genuine comfort. Our story is woven into every fiber, rooted in the belief that true luxury is found in unwavering quality and enduring design.</p><p>Our commitment begins with a foundation of absolute purity. We exclusively use 100% long-staple organic cotton, chosen for its exceptional softness and intrinsic strength. Grown without pesticides and free from harmful toxins, our textiles are naturally hypoallergenic and gentle, ensuring every touch is as safe and clean as it is comforting. This is the heart of our promise: uncompromising purity from seed to skin.</p><p>We believe true quality must be transparent and responsible. Our materials are sourced through sustainable supply chains where every partner is chosen for their dedication to ethical practices. From farms that use regenerative methods to cultivate our cotton, to the mills that process our fibers with respect for the earth, we build relationships that honor both people and the planet. This mindful, traceable approach ensures that every MIORA piece is not only beautifully made but ethically sound.</p><p>This dedication extends to every detail of your experience. We craft each MIORA essential to blend seamlessly into your life, enhancing your daily rituals with a touch of profound softness and an understated elegance. This journey is completed with our eco-conscious packaging, which uses recycled and recyclable materials to minimize our environmental footprint.</p><p>MIORA is more than an essential; it’s a choice for a more considered, comfortable, and conscious way of living. It's an invitation to elevate your daily rituals, knowing that every choice we make reflects our unwavering dedication to your well-being and the planet.</p>",
            "text_size": "text-base"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "subheading_jMcf6E",
