            "subheading": "Showroom",
            "description": "<p>The dining room is a gathering place to come together and connect over cooking and conversation. Whether hosting a dinner party for friends or enjoying a mid-week meal with family, its ambiance sets the tone for memorable experiences – and it is here where rituals and traditions are upheld.</p>",
